## Datadog — Baseline Instrumentation

These are always active (no configuration needed):
- **APM**: Auto-instrumented on all services. Distributed traces propagate across service boundaries.
- **Logs**: JSON on stdout, collected by the Datadog Agent. Correlated with traces via dd.trace_id/dd.span_id.
- **Infrastructure**: Container metrics and host metrics via the Agent.
{{#if frontend}}
- **RUM**: Browser SDK initialized. Sessions captured and connected to backend traces.
